yle=\"display: block; font-size: 26px; color: rgb(149, 25, 27);\">。</strong></span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 38px; text-align: center; margin: 24px -2px 0px;\"><span style=\"display: block; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(57, 43, 32); margin-bottom: 10px;\">cēn</span><strong style=\"display: block; font-size: 26px; color: rgb(149, 25, 27);\">参</strong></span><span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 38px; text-align: center; margin: 24px -2px 0px;\"><span style=\"display: block; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(57, 43, 32); margin-bottom: 10px;\">cī</span><strong style=\"display: block; font-size: 26px; color: rgb(149, 25, 27);\">差</strong></span><span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 38px; text-align: center; margin: 24px -2px 0px;\"><span style=\"display: block; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(57, 43, 32); margin-bottom: 10px;\">xìng</span><strong style=\"display: block; font-size: 26px; color: rgb(149, 25, 27);\">荇</strong></span><span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 38px; text-align: center; margin: 24px -2px 0px;\"><span style=\"display: block; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(57, 43, 32); margin-bottom: 10px;\">cài</span><strong style=\"display: block; font-size: 26px; color: rgb(149, 25, 27);\">菜</strong></span><span class=\"ly_fuhao\" style=\"display: inline-block; width: 26px; text-align: center; margin: 24px -2px 0px;\"><span style=\"display: block; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(57, 43, 32); margin-bottom: 10px;\">，</span><strong style=\"display: block; font-size: 26px; color: rgb(149, 25, 27);\">，</strong></span><span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 38px; text-align: center; margin: 24px -2px 0px;\"><span style=\"display: block; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(57, 43, 32); margin-bottom: 10px;\">zuǒ</span><strong style=\"display: block; font-size: 26px; color: rgb(149, 25, 27);\">左</strong></span><span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 38px; text-align: center; margin: 24px -2px 0px;\"><span style=\"display: block; font-si